      <title>莫桑比克国防部长警告有人图谋夺权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/mozambique-s-defense-minister-warns-of-a-plot-to-seize-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克国防部长警告称，在该国有争议的选举之后，不明身份的人正准备试图夺取政权，而邻国南非则因边境爆发暴力抗议活动而关闭了一条重要的金属贸易路线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/mozambique-s-defense-minister-warns-of-a-plot-to-seize-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 15:51:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚部长因车站屋顶倒塌事故辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/serbian-minister-resigns-after-deadly-roof-collapse-at-station</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，塞尔维亚一座火车站的顶棚倒塌造成 14 人死亡，该火车站由欧洲和中国公司于两年前重建。随后，塞尔维亚建设部长辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/serbian-minister-resigns-after-deadly-roof-collapse-at-station</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 11:40:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普淡化对暴力的担忧，哈里斯在电台上大肆宣传</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/us-voting-day-is-here-at-last-after-a-bruising-2024-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯在选举日努力赢得摇摆州选民的支持，而前总统唐纳德·特朗普表示他的支持者不会采取暴力行动，美国人纷纷前往投票站投票，这是美国现代史上最激烈的竞选之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/us-voting-day-is-here-at-last-after-a-bruising-2024-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
